title: Club Jeunesse Ben Guerir
text: Chabab Ben Guerir is a <a href="Morocco">Moroccan</a> <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> club currently playing in the <a href="GNF%202">second division</a>. Club Jeunesse Ben Guerir (CJBG) was founded in 1952 and is located in the town of <a href="Ben%20Guerir">Ben Guerir, Morocco</a>. They play in the Stade Municipal Ben Guerir.
